s-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Safe the date and adjust your itinerary with the current Komodo National Park reopening policy.</span><br style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">We miss you and see you soon!</span></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>','<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n</html>','20200924121153.jpg','pembukaan-taman-nasional-komodo','2020-09-24','reguler',0,'2020-09-24 12:09:38','2022-11-09 01:14:23'),(20,'BPOLBF','Loh Buaya Kembali Dibuka untuk Wisatawan',NULL,NULL,'<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">alo Sobat Floratama,</span><br style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Yang udah ga sabar pengen liburan ke Labuan Bajo dan ketemu Komodo mana suaranya??</span><br style=\"color: #262626; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', R